19:["$","p",null,{"children":["Operationally, the boostback burn’s success means SpaceX can now focus on refining turnover times between flights. If the booster’s thermal protection and engine health hold up after multiple cycles, the company’s internal target of ",["$","em",null,{"children":"daily"}]," Starship launches by 2026 starts to look plausible—not as marketing, but as milestone."]}]
